des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us by email : support@hatsy-enterprise.com

HATSY products help you control home appliances. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your bedroom lights.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your bedroom lights - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.

After connecting Alexa to your HATSY products in a few simple steps:

(1). Download our "HATSY" app in the android or ios app market;
(2). Register one tuya account in our "HATSY" app;
(3). You need to have some HATSY devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "HATSY" app and change the appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "HATSY Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, iOS, or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "HATSY Smart " skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "HATSY Smart ", and you'll be navigated to the "HATSY" login page;
(9). Input your HATSY account username and password, you'll be redirected to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
